    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白。我先确认一下结构：您说的是三个主要节点对吧？学生数据库出现两次——一次作为认证入口，一次作为GPO数据源？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Education_StudentDB",
        "adcli",
        "adcon"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，逻辑上是同一个数据库，但在流程里扮演两个角色：前端认证和后端策略存储。内容CDN在中间做协调。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Education_StudentDB",
        "Education_ContentCDN",
        "adcli",
        "adcon",
        "adsys"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我先把三个节点摆出来：adcli是学生认证端，adsys是内容CDN核心，adcon连回学生数据库做策略拉取。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "adcli",
        "adsys",
        "adcon",
        "Education_StudentDB",
        "Education_ContentCDN"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "连线关系这样：学生端先向CDN发起认证，CDN再去数据库获取GPO策略，解析后把相关策略返回给CDN，最后CDN把解析结果应用回学生端。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "authenticate user",
        "fetch GPOs",
        "relevant GPOs resolved",
        "parse GPOs and apply"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "画好了。adcli到adsys是\"authenticate user\"，adsys到adcon是\"fetch GPOs\"，然后adcon返回\"relevant GPOs resolved\"给adsys，最后adsys到adcli是\"parse GPOs and apply\"。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "adcli",
        "adsys",
        "adcon",
        "authenticate user",
        "fetch GPOs",
        "relevant GPOs resolved",
        "parse GPOs and apply"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "最后那条箭头方向好像反了？应该是CDN解析完策略后，把配置应用到学生端，所以adsys指向adcli是对的，但我刚才说的\"返回给CDN\"容易误解。确认一下：adsys→adcli是\"parse GPOs and apply\"，没错。",
      "elements_involved": [
